By Chibuike Nwabuko Abuja (Sundiata Post) Former Minister of Aviation and Peoples Democratic Party(PDP) chieftain, Chief Femi Fani-Kayode has said that Nigerians need not be surprised about  President Muhammadu Buhari’s victory at the election petition tribunal simply because not only was the election rigged, the court was also rigged. Speaking when he took to his Twitter handle
@realFFK, Fani-Kayode concluded by saying that the Buhari-led administration
controls all the three arms of government in Nigeria. His words: If anyone is surprised by today’s ruling in the @Atiku/MBuhari case then they still don’t understand the nature of the beast we are fighting and the gravity of the situation we are in. They didn’t just rig the election, they rigged the courts too! They control ALL 3 arms of Govt.! See what he tweeted: If anyone is surprised by
today’s ruling in the @Atiku/@MBuharicase
then they still don’t understand the nature of the beast we are fighting and
the gravity of the situation we are in.They didn’t just rig the election,they
rigged the courts too!They control ALL 3 arms of Govt.!